Wildrider/Sinnertwin


Wildrider emerges from the base, his face still all torn up, but if it
wasnt, he would have his jaw on the ground. "Terrorcons, how did you?" He
then sees the Quintesson, "Whats he doing here?" Wildrider asks, in
suprisingly serious tone as he points his scatterblaster cannon at the
creature, "Filthy organic"


Sinnertwin finally rights himself,but gets knocked over by Hung-grr's shot,
so he has to right himself again. One head looks up at Cutthroat, the other
at Blot, "Maybe we fight later" One head starts, "after we find good
target" the other finishes, as Sinnertwin transforms into his sleek robot
mode.
